          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Peralatan Pembinaan</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>• Jengkaut (1-40 tan)</li>
            <li>• Jentera Tanah</li>
            <li>• Backhoe Loader</li>
